  "detailed_description": "In Brave Trial, the newbie spawn point is still in the Light Boat spaceship, but this mission will be very crazy, in the arena of the target planet, there will be a large number of monsters entering the ground, but don't worry, I have enough weapons for you, you can summon allies during the battle, and fight alongside you. Once you successfully pass the tenth wave of attacks, the game will turn on endless mode, and if you like light ROUGE, you will also love this VR game.",
  "about_the_game": "In Brave Trial, the newbie spawn point is still in the Light Boat spaceship, but this mission will be very crazy, in the arena of the target planet, there will be a large number of monsters entering the ground, but don't worry, I have enough weapons for you, you can summon allies during the battle, and fight alongside you. Once you successfully pass the tenth wave of attacks, the game will turn on endless mode, and if you like light ROUGE, you will also love this VR game.",
